Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}策儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘表果然有皇室之风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}言而有信 忠义厚道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.41,0:00:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们以前真是错待他了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.28,0:00:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊父亲 我也没有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘表竟然这么讲义气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.59,0:00:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘表今日之恩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将来我们必当加倍回报
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}待回江东后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.00,0:00:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你立刻把
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们以前缴获荆州的所有兵马
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全部送还给他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.90,0:01:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再送他两千石粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}五百匹绸缎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以后逢年过节 婚嫁寿诞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们都要以礼相贺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}荆州军有埋伏 小心埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.61,0:01:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}荆州军有埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小心 保护主公 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快 大家退到舱里去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.51,0:01:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲 不要乱 不要乱 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.89,0:01:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲 保护主公
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保护主公
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.40,0:02:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.71,0:02:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是荆州兵袭击了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.31,0:02:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.21,0:02:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要慌乱 用力划桨 冲出航道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}坚持住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.89,0:02:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大家用力划桨 冲出航道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}荆州军肯定在水下设下了巨石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}堵塞了航道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们冲不出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.01,0:02:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}弃船登陆 跟刘表拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟刘表拼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.92,0:03:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}江东战船都已陷入绝境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们是上天无路入地无门哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这可是千载难逢的良机啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们必须把孙坚父子彻底消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.19,0:03:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绝不能留后患哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟我上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.39,0:03:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驾 驾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.29,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}盾牌阵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀 杀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.21,0:04:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹你不能死啊 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.79,0:04:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿啊 别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.50,0:04:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.40,0:04:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}权儿你说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}传国玉玺果真带来了灾难哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:05:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今日此事尤可见世事凶险
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.41,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}人心恶毒 人心恶毒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.22,0:05:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 儿记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.72,0:05:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公 我们快快登岸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 儿扶你上岸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.80,0:05:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹今天就不陪你上岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.51,0:05:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我的权儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你才智不凡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将来一定要好好辅佐你的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 你放心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.82,0:05:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孩儿以后会好好辅佐哥哥的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.33,0:05:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们最可怕的敌人不是刘表
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是袁绍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.90,0:06:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不久前我还为他出生入死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}屡立战功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.51,0:06:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}转眼间他就唆使刘表害我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那个传国玉玺咱们不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱们不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.13,0:06:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}改日把它转交给 转交给袁术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让他们袁氏兄弟相争去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 儿记住了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}权儿啊 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹舍不得你 爹舍不得你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:07:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公 你放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}黄盖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.93,0:07:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把权儿带走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 不要啊 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公 那你呢 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}走 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 你不要啊 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.03,0:08:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.10,0:08:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}快撤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}荆州兵把主公带走了 驾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子不要追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子不能再追了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.21,0:09:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.22,0:09:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公已留下遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子不能再追了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子 放开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.82,0:09:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子保护江东要紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 他已经归天啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.03,0:09:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹 爹 二公子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.73,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥 爹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.94,0:09:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你不要再追啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.81,0:10:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹爹临终前嘱咐过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让你一定要保住江东
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要不然他老人家在九泉之下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都不得安生啊 哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请主公三思 以大局为重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请主公三思 以大局为重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公三思 以大局为重
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.54,0:11:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子 将士们已经收拾停当
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}该启程了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}父亲的尸首现在还没有找回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.52,0:11:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}作为儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我如何向我母亲交待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我有何脸面回去见江东父老
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.53,0:11:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}事已至此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.93,0:11:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们只能先回江东了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.23,0:11:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}待日后再找刘表算账
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.94,0:11:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不找回我父亲的尸首
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我誓死不回江东
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.61,0:11:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子啊 我有一策不知可行否
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}荆州上将黄祖被你擒获
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们何不用他换回主公的尸首
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不过须有一人为使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}携黄祖前去向刘表议和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.03,0:12:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如此才有可能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你现在已经是江东之主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}绝不能再陷于险地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还是我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我是父亲的长子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.61,0:12:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.82,0:12:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘表怎么能相信我们议和的诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.22,0:12:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们杀了你怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.22,0:12:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们已经害死了主公
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.02,0:12:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正盼望着斩草除根
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.22,0:12:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以绝后患哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥 我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我也是父亲的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我去跟刘表议和
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.94,0:12:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们总该相信我们的诚意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎么能让你一个小孩子去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}公子 末将觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.62,0:13:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}权公子的话有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}首先 他是主公之子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.22,0:13:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}足见江东诚意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此外 只要大公子在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.13,0:13:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘表断不敢加害二公子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因为他们既害怕公子你复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.03,0:13:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也担心激起天下诸侯的共怒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以 以权公子为使
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}反而会安全
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可权儿只有九岁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.44,0:13:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}九岁怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘表那个老头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}见了我这个九岁的娃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道不惊讶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.05,0:13:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道不感动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}难道还怕他杀了我不成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}权公子真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.02,0:13:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}句句说在点子上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看哪 以权公子这样的才智
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此行必能成功
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}二弟 那你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}领命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.04,0:14:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}程普 黄盖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.24,0:14:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}带领所有的将士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}埋伏在荆州大营附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}接应孙权
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.95,0:14:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.22,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}蔡瑁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们和江东之仇永世不可解了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.43,0:14:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各地的诸侯听说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也会谴责我刘表不仁不义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}事情已经做下就不必后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.94,0:15:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再说了 乱世之中强者为尊哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.14,0:15:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}江东恨我们怕什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们经此大败
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经不是我们荆州的对手了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}报
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀主公
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}江东派来使者请和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}并送回黄祖将军
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.13,0:15:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么 使者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.53,0:15:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让他们进来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公 末将
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.64,0:15:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}末将回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}江东的使者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙坚之子孙权拜见刘伯伯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你就是使者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀刘伯伯 孙权今年九岁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:16:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}九岁就来为使 真是可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀刘伯伯 高祖皇帝九岁时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}射死过一头金额猛虎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.74,0:16:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}武帝爷九岁时已经挽弓杀敌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我孙权无用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.55,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}九岁时只能向刘伯伯请和
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请伯伯赐还我爹爹的尸首
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.35,0:16:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}从今以后江东永远不向荆州复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.56,0:16:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这 主公
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.23,0:16:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公 江东新败 孙坚亡命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其子年幼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们干脆斩草除根
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}彻底灭掉孙氏家族
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后乘其不备发兵直取江东
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.44,0:16:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}以成王侯大业
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘伯伯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我哥哥孙策已经继承父位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}领长沙太守
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}现在他不在三津渡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早已返回江东整军御敌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我明白你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙权啊 我要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.06,0:17:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你父亲死在我的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你江东军为何不来杀我报仇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}反而要来求和
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.84,0:17:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀刘伯伯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.04,0:17:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹爹临终前交待过我一句话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.11,0:17:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹爹说 刘伯伯有皇室之风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.65,0:17:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忠义厚道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是袁绍逼着他们伏击我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要复仇应该找袁绍复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}江东与袁绍誓不两立
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}爹爹还说为了江东的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.66,0:17:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我们应该与刘伯伯化干戈为玉帛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}两家修好和睦相处
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.13,0:17:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你父亲真是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孩子 孩子 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你父亲的尸骨我已经装殓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.24,0:17:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你可以带回江东
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.65,0:17:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我还要在江边设祭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}送别你父亲的英灵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}谢 谢刘伯伯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.13,0:18:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国 相国
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国 相国
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大喜啊 大喜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国的劲敌孙坚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在归乡的路上途经三津渡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}中了荆州军的埋伏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被刘表杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.95,0:18:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}孙坚死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真的死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.66,0:18:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}当真死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}苍天有眼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去掉了咱家一块心腹大患哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在各路诸侯当中孙坚是个英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只要他一死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}中原的诸侯都是猪狗鸡鸭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看他哪一个敢出来跟咱家做对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这回咱家可以睡一个太平觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀相国 在下有一言压抑日久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如鲠在喉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}已经是不吐不快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.94,0:19:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.04,0:19:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}敬请相国进九五之尊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即天子大位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}等等 等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是说想让咱家做皇帝 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那能成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.66,0:19:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有何不成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自相国进京后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先是扫除宫闱奸党
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}澄清朝纲 扶立新君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.54,0:20:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}继而又剿灭袁绍十八路贼军
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}君臣是无不额首称庆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}百姓无不望天颂扬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.35,0:20:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正所谓巍巍此功 功垂千古
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.55,0:20:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}锵锵英名 留芳万世
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果 如果相国不即天子位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岂不有负臣民久乱而望治之心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}汉延绵四百年 气数已尽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早就应该改朝换代了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如今放眼天下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.47,0:20:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有谁 还有谁比相国你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.74,0:20:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更配承天即位做皇帝呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}李儒你的这份心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家是极为感动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只是 各路诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.16,0:20:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如是听说咱家是做了皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他们会不会忌恨咱家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.46,0:20:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}会不会起兵闹事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}满朝百官会不会认咱们这个天子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.44,0:21:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相国 相国你多虑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}自古以来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都是为帝者先坐上龙椅之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.85,0:21:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再迫使那些不尊奉者为尊奉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不服气者为服气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.45,0:21:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果相国想慎重从事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.76,0:21:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也可以分两步走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这第一 先尊奉为尚父
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}进出用天子仪仗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.47,0:21:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第二 敕令以圣旨颁发
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这样一来也可以看看各路诸侯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.14,0:21:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}与朝中百官作何反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之后再更进一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.05,0:21:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即皇帝大位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这尚父是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就如同当今天子的爹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.87,0:22:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那李儒你的意思是说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}让咱家先做一下太上皇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.87,0:22:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然后再做皇上 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.07,0:22:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}正是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好啊 这个名目好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.55,0:22:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}李儒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看来你真是个好谋士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.96,0:22:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就有劳你来传达一下咱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 要传一下尚父的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.27,0:22:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说咱家明日正午
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.37,0:22:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要宴请各位百官
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}并给他们加官晋爵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.88,0:22:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请各位百官统统赴宴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.35,0:22:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣遵旨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.65,0:23:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有 李儒听旨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.25,0:23:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家即刻拜你为朝廷大司空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}位居三公
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣谢恩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}李大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.28,0:23:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请请请
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}李大人 请
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.25,0:23:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.25,0:23:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杨大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.55,0:23:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}刘大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.86,0:23:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕将军 请
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.16,0:23:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕将军
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.46,0:23:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.37,0:24:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看看董相国这片私宅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.87,0:24:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比大汉宫廷都要壮丽十倍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.27,0:24:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}董相他为了造这座郿坞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.18,0:24:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}调集了三十万民夫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.68,0:24:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}耗尽了朝廷库银
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.18,0:24:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他还把宫女和嫔妃
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.75,0:24:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都调到这里来供他淫乐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.05,0:24:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}此外
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.05,0:24:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他还在郿坞囤积了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.46,0:24:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}足够食用二十年的粮谷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.96,0:24:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驻守有八万精兵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.46,0:24:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王大人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.76,0:24:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这郿坞虽说是风花雪月之地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.67,0:24:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可也是天下第一重镇哪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.57,0:24:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.77,0:25:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看来董相国是要在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.07,0:25:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}安享人生极乐呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.48,0:25:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他董贼不死 低声
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.18,0:25:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大汉必亡啊 低声
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.18,0:25:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请 请 好好好 请
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.75,0:25:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各位爱卿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.95,0:25:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}袁绍的十八路贼军被咱家是
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.96,0:25:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}统统打垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.46,0:25:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}贼将孙坚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.36,0:25:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也被咱西凉将士给斩杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.66,0:25:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各州的刺史 太守们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.77,0:25:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}纷纷上表称贺
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.37,0:25:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}中原大地是一片平安哪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.18,0:25:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恭喜相国 恭喜尚父
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.08,0:25:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尚父平叛护国真是古今罕见
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.95,0:25:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}堪与日月同辉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.76,0:25:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣张温敬颂尚父万寿无疆
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.06,0:25:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哪里 哪里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.56,0:26:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寡人只是和各位爱卿同福同喜
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.17,0:26:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}寡人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.87,0:26:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尚父为国建此殊勋
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.27,0:26:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}足见天意所归 大势所趋
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.38,0:26:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣请求尚父承天意顺民心
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.98,0:26:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}改元开国即天子位
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.08,0:26:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}张爱卿
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.68,0:26:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你觉得咱家做皇上合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.09,0:26:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}合适 合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.06,0:26:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果尚父不肯做皇上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.06,0:26:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}反而是上忤天意 下负民心
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.16,0:26:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就不合适了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.96,0:26:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣请求尚父为国为民着想
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.17,0:26:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}即大位创新朝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.27,0:26:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}张爱卿你对咱家可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.78,0:26:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一片忠肝义胆哪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.48,0:26:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么这个事儿
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.98,0:26:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}各位爱卿是怎么看哪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.16,0:27:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.88,0:27:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}张爱卿劝咱家做皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.68,0:27:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真可谓是一片忠肝义胆哪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.39,0:27:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}臣只是不避荣辱直言尽忠而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.06,0:27:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可不知道你这副忠肝义胆
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.17,0:27:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}取出来下酒如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.57,0:27:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.28,0:27:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.98,0:27:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拿下
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.78,0:27:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喏
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.58,0:27:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尚父 臣无罪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.38,0:27:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尚父 臣忠心耿耿啊尚父
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.98,0:28:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}尚父 臣无罪啊 尚父
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.39,0:28:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}列位爱卿不要惊慌
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.49,0:28:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}张温这厮
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.46,0:28:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}表面上劝咱家做皇帝
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.16,0:28:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可暗地里却勾结袁氏兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.87,0:28:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}想取咱首级
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.57,0:28:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这不 刚刚袁氏有密信来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.38,0:28:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被咱哨骑截住
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.38,0:28:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不知道在座的众爱卿当中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.48,0:28:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}还有谁像张温那样
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.89,0:28:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}表面上忠顺
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.19,0:28:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}背地里却勾结叛逆
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.69,0:28:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}图谋取咱首级
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.19,0:28:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.80,0:28:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.47,0:28:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是有的话
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.27,0:28:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家可是一眼就能看出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.39,0:29:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上酒
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.59,0:29:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}按照咱凉州将士的规矩
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.69,0:29:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}对待那些叛逆者
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.89,0:29:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要枭其首 寝其皮
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.80,0:29:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}食其肉 饮其血
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.27,0:29:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}列位爱卿都是高雅之士
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.17,0:30:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这食肉寝皮之事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.27,0:30:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}咱家就替列位免了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.68,0:30:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那么各位只要是仅稍用此酒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.08,0:30:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}便可表明心意
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.59,0:30:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.87,0:30:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是甜美无比回味无穷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.97,0:30:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好酒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.88,0:30:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们 请啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.17,0:31:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}王司徒大人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.67,0:31:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这酒的味道如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.08,0:31:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.68,0:31:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.59,0:31:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真好
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.09,0:31:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}酸不酸
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.79,0:31:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来呀 让司徒大人再饮三杯
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.50,0:31:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一醉方休
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.58,0:31:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}请
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.89,0:31:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.70,0:32:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公 这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.30,0:32:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小姐 貂蝉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.48,0:32:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.88,0:32:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禽兽 我不是人 禽兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.29,0:32:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父小心
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.69,0:32:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不是人 我不是人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.80,0:32:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我与禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.40,0:32:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我与禽兽绝不 绝不两立
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.88,0:32:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.98,0:32:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我生不能杀你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.08,0:33:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我死也要向你索命
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.59,0:33:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父是在诅咒董卓那个老贼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.09,0:33:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他不但是个禽兽
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.90,0:33:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他把公卿大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.10,0:33:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}把我也逼成禽兽了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.60,0:33:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉哪
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.11,0:33:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我王允本是书香门弟
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.98,0:33:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}三代为臣 忠义一世 清白平生
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.88,0:33:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是今天 今天
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.79,0:33:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}今天我却满嘴的血腥
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.90,0:33:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}身为臣子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.20,0:33:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}受禽兽之辱却不能反杭
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.01,0:33:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}视天子蒙尘
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.68,0:34:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我却苟且偷生
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.48,0:34:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我王允连禽兽都不如啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.89,0:34:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我生不如死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.49,0:34:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.39,0:34:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你担当着兴国兴邦的大业
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.30,0:34:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}万万不可有轻生的念头啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.40,0:34:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你看天子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.70,0:34:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他小小年纪受了那么多的苦难
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.50,0:34:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}荣辱不惊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.41,0:34:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果你撇下他一走了之
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.91,0:34:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你在九泉之下如何面对先帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.59,0:34:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}先帝啊 先帝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.99,0:34:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣向你请罪了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.90,0:34:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老臣 义父
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.90,0:34:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.10,0:34:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.40,0:35:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.61,0:35:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主公
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.41,0:35:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}何事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.91,0:35:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕布前来拜见
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.09,0:35:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}定是董卓派他前来拿我了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.00,0:35:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}扶我起来
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.30,0:35:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}更衣
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.60,0:35:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要堂堂正正地赴死
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.38,0:35:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 主公 吕布是来送礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.02,0:35:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}送礼
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.28,0:35:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是给貂蝉小姐送生日礼物的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.39,0:35:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就大堂拜茶
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.50,0:36:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.61,0:36:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉 今日是你的生日吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.71,0:36:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是 今天是小女的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.09,0:36:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这事儿连我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.09,0:36:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他吕布怎么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.80,0:36:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是你 是你告诉他的 说
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.60,0:36:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你们有何苟且之事
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.51,0:36:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.79,0:37:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕将军 我家主公请将军稍候
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.70,0:37:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他这就出来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.60,0:37:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}貂蝉小姐在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.90,0:37:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在 在
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.71,0:37:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}来人哪 给将军拜茶
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.71,0:37:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父恕罪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.61,0:37:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小女
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.81,0:37:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小女与将军绝无苟且之事
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.22,0:37:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那他为何如此待你
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.79,0:37:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}禀义父 你没在家的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.59,0:37:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕将军已经来过好几次了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.80,0:37:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么 我怎么一点都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.40,0:37:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他为何而来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.31,0:37:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}上次在迁都的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.11,0:37:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吕将军救了小女之后
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.91,0:37:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就经常托故而来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.31,0:37:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}每次都带些米面
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.92,0:38:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}酒水和绫罗绸缎
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.22,0:38:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我说最近家里不缺吃穿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.89,0:38:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原来是他送的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.60,0:38:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}百官奄奄待毙
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.50,0:38:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他吕布为何独独送我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.81,0:38:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我明白了 原来你
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.70,0:38:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女儿 请受老夫一拜
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.10,0:38:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 你这是干什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.10,0:38:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}万万使不得 请起 请起
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.60,0:38:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女儿啊 你要不答应我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.71,0:38:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫就长跪不起
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.51,0:39:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 我答应 我答应
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.61,0:39:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什么事情我全都答应
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.51,0:39:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}粉身碎骨绝不推辞
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.52,0:39:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}求女儿救救大汉
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.52,0:39:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}救救天下苍生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.52,0:39:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我一个弱女子
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.92,0:39:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如何救得了大汉和天下苍生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.00,0:39:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.60,0:39:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你只要答应一个救就成了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.40,0:39:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要不然老夫宁肯跪死也绝不起身
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.41,0:39:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我答应 我答应
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.01,0:39:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}义父 快快请起
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.42,0:39:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.02,0:39:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}老夫想让你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.93,0:39:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喜欢上吕布 成吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.50,0:39:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}成不成啊 我
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.80,0:40:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你说啊 成不成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.61,0:40:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小女
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.51,0:40:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小女怕配不上吕将军
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.12,0:40:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我糊涂了 我老糊涂了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.62,0:40:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好 好 真是天作之合啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.57,0:40:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}可是这跟救大汉有什么关系呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.49,0:40:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这个老夫日后会和你说的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.32,0:40:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这会儿我得去会客了 好 好
